          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I know what size to choose?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The sizing of Arms of Andes products is based on the international sizing system and you can see the basis of these sizes in our <a href=\"https://armsofandes.com/pages/size-guide-men-and-women\" target=\"_blank\">Size Guide</a>.</p>",
