            "content": "<p>Please allow 2 business days after the date of purchase for handling. <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Delivery within the USA  can take 2-7 business days</strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">. </span>We deliver from Los Angeles, CA, so all items have already passed US customs. </p>",
