            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>We can ship to almost any location worldwide</strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">. </span>In the USA and Canada, shipping for orders under US$200 is calculated based on the package weight, while orders over US$200 include free shipping. For shipping to Europe and the United Kingdom, please visit our <a href=\"https://armsofandes.eu/\" target=\"_blank\">European site</a>. Shipping to the rest of the world usually costs around US$25, depending on the weight of your order.</p>",
