            "heading": "How are refunds processed?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Once the item you are returning is received and inspected, we will send you an email to notify you and confirm if the refund will be approved. After approval, the corresponding amount will be credited to credit card or original method of payment,within a certain amount of days.</p>",
